step 1: create project folder 

step 2: open command promt and create environment using following command

   1st: python -m venv . (This will create environment in current folder)
      : cd scripts
      : activate
      : cd..
   2nd: pip install scikit-learn (it will install scikit-learn in env)
      : pip install streamlit (if you need other libraries you can install via pip)

step 3: copy paste all files in project folder
      : if you want to modify the code you can modify 
      : open the .py file and run it without debugging
